# diQalamos Website

Professional website for Digital Humanities engineering services by Serhat AÃ§ar.

## Project Structure
- `index.html` - Main HTML file
- `css/` - Stylesheets
  - `style.css` - Main styles
  - `animations.css` - Animation styles
  - `responsive.css` - Responsive design
- `js/` - JavaScript files
  - `main.js` - Core functionality
  - `animations.js` - Animation scripts
  - `components.js` - Interactive components
- `images/` - Image assets (add your images here)
- `README.md` - This file

## Setup Instructions
1. Download all files maintaining the folder structure
2. Upload to your web hosting service
3. Update contact information in `index.html` if needed
4. Replace placeholder images in `images/` folder with your own:
   - `logo.svg` - Your logo
   - `favicon.ico` - Website favicon
   - `hero-bg.jpg` - Hero section background image

## Features
- Fully responsive design
- Interactive animations
- Professional Digital Humanities portfolio
- SEO optimized
- Accessible design

